Blood is thicker than water.

39:40.880 --> 39:42.210
So, you love me, huh?

39:42.210 --> 39:43.540
♪ Gotta leave the past,
it's in the past ♪

39:43.540 --> 39:46.040
It means the family
you're born into

39:46.040 --> 39:48.960
